                <ul class="text-sm text-red-200/70 list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
                  <li>Never store plain-text passwords - always use ARGON2_HASH</li>
                  <li>Never log or expose password hashes in API responses</li>
                  <li>Use HTTPS for all authentication endpoints</li>
                  <li>Implement rate limiting on login attempts</li>
                </ul>
