              <div>
                <h4 class="text-orange-300 font-bold mb-1 text-sm">Do NOT use MD5/SHA256 for passwords!</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-orange-200/70">
                  MD5 and SHA256 are too fast for password hashing - they can be brute-forced easily. Always use ARGON2_HASH for passwords.
